\define icn(icon)
<button class="tc-btn-invisible"> {{$icon$}}</button>
\end

A button (<<icn $:/core/images/highlight>>) for the Editor toolbar that highlights a selection<br>
Assigned shortcut: {{$:/config/shortcuts/highlight}}

''Note::'' $:/plugins/tg/highlight-button/style contains the applied 'highlight' class `tgy`:

```
.tgy {
     background-color:Yellow;
}
```
